response: You can register for courses through the student portal at portal.university.edu. Log in with your student ID and password, then navigate to the Registration section.

prompt: How do I contact financial aid?
response: You can contact the Financial Aid office at financialaid@university.edu or call (555) 123-4567. Office hours are Monday-Friday 8AM-5PM.

prompt: What wifi network should I use?
response: Students should connect to the 'UniversityWiFi' network using their student credentials. For guest access, use 'UniversityGuest' network.

prompt: I can't log into my account
response: For login issues, please visit the IT Help Desk in the Technology Center or call (555) 123-HELP. Have your student ID ready.
